## 初步扫描结论\n以下是基于数据的初步定位结论：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency in normal vs anomaly durations observed, suggesting bottleneck.\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"normal_avg_duration\": 9988.60,\n        \"anomaly_avg_duration\": 78460.53,\n        \"latency_multiplier\": 7.85,\n        \"linked_traces\": [\"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"High upstream latency observed in interaction with ProductCatalogService; issue might either be propagated or local.\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"normal_avg_duration\": 156733.33,\n        \"anomaly_avg_duration\": 6203919.00,\n        \"latency_multiplier\": 39.59,\n        \"linked_traces\": [\"frontend->checkoutservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"]\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\n下一步建议从异常传播关系入手，通过详细分析 ProductCatalogService 涉及的所有调用来验证此初步假设。"}
